STEALTH "STEALTH SKILL"

Stealth is the skill tree for all things secret, hidden, or shadow. Little is
known about its practitioners. Rumors swirl of an underground group of thieves
called the Guild, though no one dares confirm them.

(To begin your journey down the path of Stealth, try bribing the hidden guild-
master.)

See also: HIDE, SNEAK, BACKSTAB, PICKPOCKET, DISGUISE, JAB, TERRIFY,
    DARKNESS, APPRAISAL, BLIND, VAULTCRACKING, POISONS, DEADLY POISONS,
    SECRET CACHE, DAGGER MASTERY, CLOAK OF DARKNESS, INFILTRATE, SAP,
    SHADOWSTEP, CONCEALMENT, ESCAPE, PRICK
#
APPRAISAL

Appraisal (Stealth ability)

Usage:  look <person>

A clever thief can see what her mark is carrying with a quick glance. When
you look at other characters, you will see their inventories.

Gain skill from this ability by attempting to look at people's inventories.

See also: CONCEALMENT
#
BACKSTAB

Backstab (Stealth ability)

Usage:  backstab [victim]
Cooldown:  9 seconds
Cost:  15 move

A brave warrior looks his foe in the eye, but a clever assassin looks his
target in the back as he strikes. You must wield a stabbing weapon to use this
ability.

Backstab deals 2x weapon damage on a successful attack, and the opponent has
no chance to dodge if the attack succeeds. A particularly skilled assassin
deals 4x weapon damage instead.

Gains experience when you use Backstab, even if it fails.
#
BLIND

Blind (Stealth ability)

Usage:  blind [victim]
Cooldown:  10 seconds
Cost:  15 move
Debuff type:  Stealth

You toss sand in your opponents' eyes, blinding them for 10 seconds. Being
unable to see your foes inflicts a penalty of -50 to To-hit, Block and Dodge.

If you're fighting, this will automatically target your opponent.

Gains experience when you use Blind, even if it fails.
#
"CLING TO SHADOW"

Cling to Shadow (Stealth ability)

With Cling to Shadow, your chance of successfully hiding (with the "hide"
command) becomes 100% and you cannot be found using the "search" ability. You
can still be found using the Sense Life and Detection rituals.

Gains experience when you hide, and when people would find you using Search.

See also: HIDE, SEARCH
#
"CLOAK OF DARKNESS"

Cloak of Darkness (Stealth ability)

This passive ability keeps you from being spotted at range on the map, and
reduces the chance of guard towers seeing you.

This ability gains experience when you would be spotted on the map, or a
tower would try to shoot you.
#
CONCEALMENT

Concealment (Stealth ability)

With proper concealment, other players can no longer see exactly what you're
using or holding.

This ability gains skill points whenever they try.
#
"CRUCIAL JAB"

Crucial Jab
Class ability: Bandit
Debuff type: Stealth

Your Jab ability causes a debuff equal to your total level divided by 80 to
your victim's Dexterity, for 10 seconds.

See also: JAB
#
DARKNESS

Darkness (Stealth ability)

Usage:  darkness
Cooldown:  15 seconds
Duration:  1 mud hour (75 seconds)
Cost:  15 move

Master the power of shadow to blanket an area in darkness. It becomes much
harder to see anything at all, even where there should be daylight. This
ability also grants the ability to see in the darkness it creates.

Gains experience when you cast Darkness.

See also: BLIND
#
"DAGGER MASTERY"

Dagger Mastery (Stealth ability)

Your attacks with stabbing weapons (such as daggers) deal 50% more damage.

Gains experience when it increases your damage.
#
DISGUISE

Disguise (Stealth ability)

Usage:  disguise <person>

A savvy rogue learns to blend into his surroundings. With this ability, you can
look like any human NPC. If you behave like one as well, you might find you
disappear into the crowd. Disguising does not always succeed, but informs you if
it fails.

Disguised players do not appear on the map.

Morphing will remove disguises.

Gain experience by trying to disguise yourself.
#
DIVERSION

Diversion
Class ability:  Smuggler
Debuff type:  Stealth
Cost:  50 move
Cooldown:  30 seconds
Usage:  diversion

You create a flashy diversion, penalizing all enemies. The first victim loses
Wits equal to your Charisma. Each additional victim loses Wits equal to half
your Charisma (rounded up) instead. This effect lasts 15 seconds.
#
ESCAPE

Escape (Stealth ability)

Usage:  escape
Cost:  10 move
Time:  5 seconds

Escape lets you run for the nearest window and quickly exit the building or
ship you're in, making a quick getaway from even the most confusing castles.

Gains experience when you escape.
#
HIDE HIDING

Hide (Stealth ability)

Usage:  hide

When you type hide there is a chance (based on your Stealth level) that you hide
in the room. If hidden you can't be seen by other people. Hide is broken by
pressing return, regardless of whether you typed a command or not.

Gains experience when you try to hide.

See also: CLING TO SHADOW, SEARCH, SNEAK, SENSE LIFE RITUAL
#
HOWL

Howl
Class ability:  Shadow Wolf
Debuff type:  Stealth
Cost:  50 move
Cooldown:  30 seconds
Usage:  howl

You let out a terrifying howl, penalizing all enemies. The first victim loses
to-hit equal to 4x your Charisma. Each additional victim loses to-hit equal to
2x Charisma instead.
